course_title: Women in the Bronze Age, Classical Greek and Hellenistic Cultures

sections.comments: Visit https://cnrs.ubc.ca/fall2020courses/ for information on course delivery.  If this course is full or blocked, please register in the wait list section.

description: The images projected in mythology, literature, and art are compared with realities of women's lives insofar as they can be reconstructed from historical, legal, and archaeological records.
